name: Michelle Yeoh
description:
A commission of @Zorglub.

Michelle Yeoh is a Malaysian actress who recently won the Academy Award for Best Actress for her role in Everything Everywhere All at Once.

Another 1000-step TI, trained on a dataset of 18 images with my usual settings.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
